<span class="index">7.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_7_2838877" id="refIndex_7_2838877" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[7]_2838877">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/698154/737eytLs4fMSdKeO8ZABrxbJDr1bKwUDs-j0bAP7-SV4uqXVmqmfRw_uim_kiCYIRFArlNg7ktuTA8hOyROea9WYGexIczw1Rly8bJB7-RtDOJ5c9pZ0" target="_blank" class="text">蝶恋花·农民工之妻<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
<span class="site">．中国知网（《词刊》 2009年09期 ）</span><span>&#91;引用日期2016-01-10&#93;</span></li><li class="reference-item reference-item--type1 " id="reference-[8]-2838877-wrap">
<span class="index">8.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_8_2838877" id="refIndex_8_2838877" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[8]_2838877">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
